00:30:54.044 --> 00:30:57.704
I think it's very context dependent, depends on the tumor

541
00:30:57.824 --> 00:31:01.604
type. And I don't think probably the viral mimicry response will

542
00:31:01.664 --> 00:31:04.464
work the same or even work in all tumors.

