00:31:57.304 --> 00:32:01.164
interferon response derived from the sensing of double-stranded RNA, but

565
00:32:01.244 --> 00:32:05.064
also the effects of the RNA-DNA hybrids, because

566
00:32:05.124 --> 00:32:08.884
these DNA-RNA hybrids are inducing replication stress, DNA

