1299
01:13:11.724 --> 01:13:15.524
And so what we think is that some of the limitations that are inherent to cancer

1300
01:13:15.564 --> 01:13:19.154
vaccine, notably the fact that when T cells come inside the tumor, they lose their

1301
01:13:19.184 --> 01:13:22.156
activity.Or, and they poorly actually infiltrate the tumor.

1302
01:13:22.646 --> 01:13:26.245
And even if they are in the tumor and they are functional, sometimes we cannot

1303
01:13:26.256 --> 01:13:28.496
